Titolo: Ark Area

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: Ark Area is a multidirectional scrolling shooter released in arcades by UPL in 1987. The player uses futuristic spacecraft to shoot enemies, collect power-ups, and defeat bosses while advancing through 23 levels. It is the sequel to the arcade game Nova 2001, which was released by Universal in the USA.

Genere: Scrolling shooter 

Valutazione: N/A
